23 that the product does not contain intentionally added perfluoroalkyl and
24 polyfluoroalkyl substances.
25 Section 23 of this bill provides that a person who willfully and knowingly
26 violates the provisions of section 21 or 22 is guilty of a misdemeanor.
27 Section 20 of this bill provides an exception to the requirements and
